entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've been a great help in putting down the Tuskan raids. Mos Eisley is a bit safer because of you.
entries.journal_entry_description: The Tusken raids have been getting worse and they need your help to put them down.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: You're a natural! I think we'll just call you The Tusken Slayer! Why, I'm sure the Tusken Warriors won't be any trouble at all for someone like you!
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Purivs is impressed with your skills and has sent you out after the most dangerous of the Tuskens. He wants  you to take out five Tusken Raider Warriors.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Purvis tells me you've done well! Come back to me and we'll finish our business.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You've handled the Tusken threat. Return to the Mayor to complete your business.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: There is a message inbound, originating at Jabba's Palace. You wonder who it could be...
entries.task06_comm_message_text: Are you still doing tasks for the mayor? Hurry up, will you? Jabba's becoming impatient!
